title: Small Catalan village strives for Catalonia's independence
description:
The Catalan village of Llivia already geographically separated from Spain nearly 500 years ago.
Now its residents are ardent supporters of Catalonia's drive for independence.
Al Jazeera’s Jonah Hull reports from Llivia.
